===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|armée||lang=fro}} (French {{term|armée|lang=fr}}), from Proto-Romance ''[[armata]]'', a noun taken from the past participle of {{etyl|la}} {{term|armare||lang=la|to [[arm]]}}.

